### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080
@phoneA = +33611111111
@phoneB = +33622222222

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Créer les utilisateurs
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Register user A
POST {{host}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Alice",
  "password": "test123",
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneA}}",
  "email": "alice.msg@test.com"
}

### 2. Register user B
POST {{host}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Bob",
  "password": "test123",
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}",
  "email": "bob.msg@test.com"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Login
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 3. Login as Alice
POST {{host}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneA}}",
  "password": "test123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ""));
%}

### 4. Login as Bob
POST {{host}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}",
  "password": "test123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("tokenB", response.body.trim().replace(/^"|"$/g, ""));
%}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### SETUP — Friendship (la conv DIRECT est créée à l'acceptation)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 5. Alice sends a friend request to Bob (captures friendshipId)
POST {{host}}/api/friendships
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "phoneNumber": "{{phoneB}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("friendshipId", response.body.id); %}

### 6. Bob accepts the request (DIRECT conv auto-created)
POST {{host}}/api/friendships/{{friendshipId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}

### 7. Alice reads her conversations to grab the conversationId
GET {{host}}/api/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("conversationId", response.body[0].conversationId);
%}


### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### ENVOI DE MESSAGES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 9. Alice envoie un message à Bob (expects 201)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Salut Bob !
--WebAppBoundary--

### 10. Bob répond à Alice (expects 201 — même conversationId)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Salut Alice, ça va ?
--WebAppBoundary--

### 11. Alice lit les messages de la conversation (expects 200 avec 2 messages)
GET {{host}}/api/messages/conversation/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### CAS LIMITES
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 12. Message exactement 500 caractères (expects 201)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"


--WebAppBoundary--

### 13. Message 501 caractères (expects 400 - validation error)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"


--WebAppBoundary--

### 14. Message vide sans fichier (expects 400)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"


--WebAppBoundary--

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### CAS D'ERREUR
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 15. Envoyer dans une conversation inexistante (expects 404)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Ce message ne partira pas
--WebAppBoundary--

### 16. Lire une conversation qui n'existe pas (expects 404)
GET {{host}}/api/messages/conversation/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. Sans token (expects 401)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Pas de token
--WebAppBoundary--

### 18. Alice envoie un message avec Texte ET Image (expects 201)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Voici la photo des vacances !
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./photo.png
--WebAppBoundary--

### 19. Bob envoie un document PDF SEUL sans texte (expects 201) — nécessite document.pdf à la racine
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="document.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./document.pdf
--WebAppBoundary--

> {%
    // Capture l'ID du message contenant la pièce jointe pour le test de suppression plus bas
    client.global.set("messageWithAttachmentId", response.body.id);
%}

### 20. Alice tente d'envoyer un format interdit (expects 400) — nécessite notes.txt à la racine
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="notes.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ./notes.txt
--WebAppBoundary--

### 21. Alice envoie un message MULTIPART vide (ni texte ni fichier - expects 400)
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="conversationId"

{{conversationId}}
--WebAppBoundary--

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### CHATAPP-13 : MODIFICATION DE MESSAGE
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 22. Alice récupère d'abord l'historique pour attraper un ID de message
GET {{host}}/api/messages/conversation/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    if (response.body && response.body.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("messageIdToEdit", response.body[0].id);
        client.global.set("bobMessageId", response.body[1].id);
    }
%}

### 23. Alice modifie son propre message (expects 200)
PUT {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageIdToEdit}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Salut Bob ! (Modifié pour corriger une faute)"
}

### 24. Alice tente de modifier le message de Bob (expects 400)
PUT {{host}}/api/messages/{{bobMessageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Je pirate ton message !"
}

### 25. Alice tente de mettre un contenu vide (expects 400)
PUT {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageIdToEdit}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": ""
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
### CHATAPP-13 : SUPPRESSION
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 26. Alice supprime son propre message (expects 200)
DELETE {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageIdToEdit}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 27. Bob tente de supprimer le message de Alice (sécurité - expects 400)
DELETE {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageIdToEdit}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}

### 28. Bob retire l'attachment de son message PDF mais garde le texte (expects 200)
DELETE {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageWithAttachmentId}}/attachment
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenB}}

### 29. Alice tente de supprimer l'attachment de Bob (sécurité - expects 400)
DELETE {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageWithAttachmentId}}/attachment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}